    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889450/extras/05b7473aaf1ede3d8e8e91169a31aa93.poster.avif?t=1770829369\" width=475 height=92 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889450/extras/05b7473aaf1ede3d8e8e91169a31aa93.webm?t=1770829369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PACK MY STUFF</strong>是一款引人入胜的益智隐藏物品游戏。您的任务是找到房间里的所有物品并将其装入箱子。这是一个简单的概念，但却非常有趣。作为搬家公司的一名员工，您要帮助Neuberg的居民搬家，将他们的物品小心翼翼地装入搬家箱中。让自己沉浸在充满活力、令人耳目一新的点击游戏中，享受田园诗般的体验。从日常生活的需求中解脱出来，享受几轮轻松愉快的<strong>PACK MY STUFF</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889450/extras/11a018be687d52e8adecd0518960f573.avif?t=1770829369\" width=444 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为搬家公司的员工，您在帮助新堡居民打包他们珍爱的物品中扮演着重要的角色。一路上，您将发现新的秘密和宝藏，同时在个人日记中记录自己的旅程。让自己沉浸在以美国一个迷人小镇为背景的《收拾我的东西》的迷人世界中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889450/extras/96103d31da7360cf3516430417f7cdb7.avif?t=1770829369\" width=444 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PACK MY STUFF的操作简单易学，让您可以直接进入游戏。您的目标是打包每个关卡中的所有物品，成功完成关卡。在您的旅途中，不要忘记对隐藏的宝藏和秘密保持警惕。从舒适的家庭住宅到广阔的仓库，您可以探索各种各样的地点。探索美国中产阶级家庭的精髓，协助收拾大大小小的公司办公室，同时沉浸在自己独特的故事中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889450/extras/8b6057e9d6634842619ccfd873667d99.poster.avif?t=1770829369\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889450/extras/8b6057e9d6634842619ccfd873667d99.webm?t=1770829369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889450/extras/8b6057e9d6634842619ccfd873667d99.mp4?t=1770829369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您喜欢用力！[/b]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那就使用我们的 &quot;困难模式 &quot;吧，在这里您没有任何帮助。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889450/extras/b82b858561594ee7a4adc21a57f0156f.avif?t=1770829369\" width=444 height=68 /></span>欢迎来到Newhill，一个风景如画、梦想成真的美国梦之城。与我们一起帮助住户收拾行李，为他们顺利入住新公寓铺平道路。成为他们旅途中的一部分，让他们梦想成真。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >获得酷炫的新盒子皮肤</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889450/extras/a63e560d9fb6ccbcf4ccc8fdc660d752.poster.avif?t=1770829369\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889450/extras/a63e560d9fb6ccbcf4ccc8fdc660d752.webm?t=1770829369\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1889450/extras/a63e560d9fb6ccbcf4ccc8fdc660d752.mp4?t=1770829369\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[列表］</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验简单而有趣的游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收拾地图上的所有物品，如桌子或电脑。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >访问的地方，如家庭住宅，办公室，仓库，花园和更多<br>[找到我们的秘密并解锁成就</p></li></ul>",
